#summary Internal representation of NUL pairs.
#labels Phase-Implementation
#sidebar ExpressionClassTree

Internal representation of NulSet.

= Description =

Syntaxes:
 * *{* value *}*
 * value1*,* value2*,* value3*,..* remainingValues

== Components ==
 * [nul_expression] `first` : The first component(s). (list head)
 * [nul_xpr_object] `second` : The remaining component(s). (list queue)

== Overrides ==

=== has ===
Redefines the condition for an object to belong to the set defined here.

=== unified ===
Unify each elements together
